data.description: This charming patio home is nestled in the lovely neighborhood of Willow Winds. Upon entry, you are greeted with warm hardwood floors, tall ceilings, and a spacious foyer. The living room features a built-in bookshelf, and a cozy fireplace, perfect for keeping you warm during chilly winter months, and the formal dining room can easily be used as an office. Enjoy cooking in the eat-in kitchen which is  adorned with stunning natural cabinets that provide ample storage space, and beautiful upgrades of tile backsplash, copper patina sink. and custom luxury CAFE appliances!  A mud/laundry room offers extra sink and storage space.  The master bedroom is complete with his and hers closets including a walk-in, and an en-suite bathroom with a double vanity, and a garden tub/shower combo. A private courtyard is the perfect place to relax, and the low maintenance enclosed yard gives you more time to relax with family and friends. There is a garage that provides convenient kitchen and courtyard entry. This highly desirable community maintains nicely tended common areas, and is located minutes away from I-26, Harbison, and Downtown Columbia where you will find an abundance of local shopping, dining and entertainment options. Don't wait! Come see this home today!
